rows.label: tlk70000061_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I swear, if Rita bawls her eyes
out for much longer, she'll end
up suffering from dehydration...

rows.label: tlk70000061_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I think she understood her father
perfectly well. But still she whines
and moans about how unfair it is.

rows.label: tlk70000061_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I almost want to burst into tears
myself, the way she's acting...

rows.label: tlk70000061_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Still, I'm dragging her out of
here at the first sign of
trouble, by force if I have to.

rows.label: tlk70000061_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I promised Zain I would.
Should anything happen, I
think we'll make for Invidia.

rows.label: tlk70000061_05_msg0006
rows.name:
Of course, I pray with all my
heart that nothing will happen,
but it pays to be cautious...
